    "The PEnKF assimilates the information in y t by first sampling",
    ") by running Algorithm 3 with parameter θ i t and ensemble members x i,1:N t-1.",
    "Finally, a new weight is constructed according to",
    "Step t of the PEnKF is summarised by Algorithm 5.",
    "Note that we include a resampling step, which is triggered if the effective sample size (ESS) falls below some user specified threshold, γM."
